meanings.definition: An organic compound with the formula C₁₀H₉N, structurally related to naphthylamine but with one amino group.
meanings.english_definition: An organic compound with the formula C₁₀H₉N, structurally related to naphthylamine but with one amino group.

etymology.value: Derived from 'semi-' (meaning half), 'naphthylamine' (referring to the naphthyl group and amine functional group).
